name: Tortilla Market Maina
description:
In tortilla market maina you are a girl in Mexico trying to get your tortillas from your house to your market, but theres trash everywhere and seagulls are trying to steal your tortillas! avoid the tortilla theirs and make a real shop!

HOW TO PLAY :

basically you a a girl and u go to your home and collect 10 tortillas

you have to bring them to your market

without the seagulls stealing them

or you tripping over piles of trash

and losing a tortilla

you have a shovel tool

every 5 seconds

by clicking on trash

you can get rid of it

your market is the red oneclick backspace or tab to go to menu
